data.description: Spacious home on a large cul-de-sac lot! This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home features 2,332 sq. ft., a family room, a 2 car garage, and RV parking. The living room has luxury vinyl plank flooring, and a wood-burning stove for additional heat in Payson's cooler months. The kitchen has plenty of counter space, a breakfast bar, a pantry, and a breakfast nook along with a formal dining area. The master suite features private access to the backyard, a walk-in closet, and a full bathroom with double sinks. Outside there is a covered front porch and in the backyard a patio, a large deck, and a shed. The expansive backyard has lots of tall pines making it feel like you're truly in the forest.  There's plenty of space for entertaining or sitting in the hot tub in the moon light.
